Author: Nihilistic_Asshole_9
Text: Thank you for the encouragement! I'm more of a binger than a restrictor, I usually just don't keep anything down so it's difficult to eat even normal portions without horrible acid reflux :/ I'm having some sushi for dinner and trying to push through it. I know I'll benefit in the long term <3

Author: wastingsleep
Text: You’re doing really well but you need to keep going and push more, especially if you’ve been restricting for a while and you’re going to exercise. You got this!
